<h3>Directions</h3>
<h4>By public transport</h4>
<p>
From Paris, take the line <u><a href="https://www.ratp.fr/en/horaires" target="_blank" style="color: #FFF">RER B</a></u> 
to Saint-Remy-lès-Chevreuse. You have three options:
<ul style="font-size:20px;">
<li> Stop at Massy-Palaiseau and take the bus number 
<u><a href="http://www.albatrans.net/les-lignes-les-horaires/horaires-ete/" target="_blank" style="color: #FFF">91.06 (A, B or C)</a></u> 
or <u><a href="http://www.albatrans.net/les-lignes-les-horaires/horaires-ete/" target="_blank" style="color: #FFF">91.10</a></u>. 
Get off at the bus stop "Université Paris-Saclay".
<li> Stop at Orsay Ville and take 
the 
<u><a href="https://www.transdev-idf.com/ligne-7/mobicaps_006/006-006" target="_blank" style="color: #FFF">bus number 7</a></u>. 
Get off at the bus stop "Université Paris-Saclay".
<li> Stop at Le Guichet and 
take the 
<u><a href="https://www.transdev-idf.com/ligne-9/les-ulis-jouy-en-josas/006-006" target="_blank" style="color: #FFF">bus number 9</a></u>. 
Get off at the bus stop "Université Paris-Saclay".
</ul>
</p>

<h4>By car</h4>

<p> 
<ul style="font-size:20px;">
<li> Departure from Paris, périphérique - Porte de Saint Cloud:
<ul style="font-size:20px;">
<li> Take the N118 towards Nantes-Bordeaux.
<li> After around 20 km, take the exit 9 "Centre Universitaire".
<li> Follow the road signs at the roundabout.
</ul>
<li> Departure from Paris via A6-A10:
<ul style="font-size:20px;">
<li> Drive towards Nantes-Bordeaux, then drive towards "Cité Scientifique" (left lane) and then Saclay.
<li> Drive on D36, then merge onto D128 and drive towards "Centre Universitaire".
<li> Drive through 2 roundabouts. 
At the third roundabout, take the first exit on the right (Gif-sur-Yvette). After 500 m, take the first exit on the left.
</ul>
<li> From the south via A10:
<ul style="font-size:20px;">
<li> Take the N118 towards Paris-Porte de Saint-Cloud.
<li> Take the exit 9 "Centre Universitaire".
<li> At the roundabout, take the first exit on the right (Gif-sur-Yvette). Then after 500 m, take the first exit on the left.
</ul>
<li> From the south via A6:
<ul style="font-size:20px;"> 
<li> Take the N104 ("Francilienne") towards Versailles until the motorway interchange with A10.
<li> Take the exit 9 "Centre Universitaire".
<li> At the roundabout, take the first exit on the right (Gif-sur-Yvette). 
Then after 500 m, take the first exit on the left.	
</ul>
<ul>
</p> -->

